| New Hire Retention Funnel | Tooltip 7: Hiring Activity |
| Hiring vs New Hire Loss (Column Chart) | Tooltip 7: Hiring Activity |
| Hiring Demand Forecast (Column + Line) | Tooltip 7: Hiring Activity |
| Hiring & Attrition Matrix by Organization | Tooltip 8: Benchmark Comparison |

### Key Insights
- "Are we hiring fast enough to replace losses?"
- "What % of new hires stay past 1 year?"
- "Which orgs need more hiring support?"
- "What's our projected hiring need for next year?"

